Plot.
Kung Pow Enter the Fist is a movie within a movie, created to spoof the martial
arts genre. Writer/director Steve Oedekerk uses contemporary characters and
splices them into a 1970s kung-fu film, weaving the new and old together. As
the main character, The Chosen One, Oedekerk sets off to avenge the deaths of
his parents at the hands of kung-fu legend Master Pain. Along the way, he
encounters some strange characters, one of which is a cow trained in the
martial arts.
